Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:11.03,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more amazing than Kamisakuramachi-Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:15.15,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know too many details myself, so don't take everything I say on the matter seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:17.76,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are lots of other dangerous people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:18.68,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:22.68,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I saw that black bike today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:25.94,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first big target in a while. A teenage girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.56,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God for that informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:32.61,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, my body began to shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:04.66,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the "reality" you're seeing... truly "reality"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.51,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery you see every time always remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:14.00,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, on your acceptance to your new school, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:17.40,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan currently faces many gloomy issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:22.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Such as the birthrate declining, on top of other things that are a cause for concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.35,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I look at all of you in attendance today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:29.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,it truly feels to me that all of you will lead Japan toward a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.77,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It really lifts my spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.12,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Undoubtedly, today is a special day for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:38.39,SUBS-ALT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But I also realize, as I stand here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:43.35,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you believe that today is just a day like any other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:43.35,SUBS-ALT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}that today is a special day for the teachers, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.49,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ry-Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:52.15,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,A reserved boy who has just arrived in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.16,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sonohara Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.63,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with a girl who seems a little as if her mind is somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.31,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kida Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:07.31,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I may seem mature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:12.21,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,but inside I'm just a fragile little fifteen-year old, just like the rest of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.80,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy boy who's always off in his own world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.73,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kamichika Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.71,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.80,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a girl who has another side to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.11,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common to have people like these around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:27.21,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Harima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.43,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima Mika? Is she absent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.56,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:39.54,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the typical scene you all have seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.45,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Late on the first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.80,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just taking care of introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.45,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce yourself, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.88,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yagiri Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:04:01.02,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, there are times where something causes reality to show you another side of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:05.02,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Yagiri... please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:05.97,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.47,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.83,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to come to school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.60,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think I'll ever be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:14.85,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.91,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I came here to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.27,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.36,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yagiri, what do you mean by...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.03,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:29.33,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very important matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.62,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any more time to mess around with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.12,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.34,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yagiri, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,An event, that disrupts the peaceful scenery and eventually throws everything into disarray,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.63,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,makes you question what you'll do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.64,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,And here, there's also a girl who has been through one of these, "events".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:53.23,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days ago, she {\i1}actually{\i0} should have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:05:00.77,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl was born in a normal household.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:05.22,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She lived a life free of worries or hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.34,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she started middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.46,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,an envelope arrived at her home, suddenly and without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.80,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What was in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.60,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.90,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows that my father is having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.30,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There was also a letter that said something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.31,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you actually think this should be forgiven?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.90,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably sent by someone who knew the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.31,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What your father did was terrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.82,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,but what the other person did was terrible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:47.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.28,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,so I just decided to hide the pictures for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.93,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, that normal and peaceful scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.76,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,began to disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.03,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you had it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.46,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only able to put up with it for about six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.77,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that things would be better if I brought everything out into the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:16.60,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to talk about it, you don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:20.92,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things I can't tell others about either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.61,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.70,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.16,SUBS-ALT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I couldn't believe that I mistook my cell phone for the remote control!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.19,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,After all of that... nothing changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.10,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if my mother chose not to talk about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:37.26,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,or if they worked things out in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:42.04,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,My father's boring jokes, and the extremely sweet taste of my mother's stew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.30,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Not one thing changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:52.77,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured, maybe I should just disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.52,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}Lately, that's all that's been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:04.12,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.32,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I'm not as far gone as you are, Magenta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.65,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.30,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,This person I was dating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.59,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,ended up leaving me for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:15.73,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.16,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who I can never bring myself to forgive is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.79,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.32,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it happens all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.71,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,and since we have to keep up appearances... not to make such a big deal about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.97,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't even one utterance of how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:35.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,So the way I saw it... she was putting our family's reputation above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:40.81,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again... I don't know... Maybe she was just looking out for my well-being in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.35,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.76,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.96,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't really care about you, Nakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.65,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably only cares about herself-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.65,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.62,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.66,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Magenta-san, would you like to disappear with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:08.52,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,If we died together, maybe they'll understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.09,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,exactly what it was they should have treasured the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.85,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look back on it now... it was a foolish choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.47,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, she felt that this is what needed to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.14,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She felt the strength of Nakura's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:29.76,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the face of the person who had the same views and feelings as she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:34.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the man were lying to her, she had nothing left to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.82,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,or so she thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.94,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Magenta-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.20,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.96,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you Nakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:55.27,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment she saw his face, she thought that this man wasn't Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:09:01.50,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she went with him because she wouldn't be able to forgive herself if she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.44,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,So when it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.82,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.51,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.26,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we all set?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.68,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:27.87,SUBS-ALT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well then... Sorry for tricking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:34.16,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock, resilience, regret... All of these emotions passed through her mind at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:40.97,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, right before she lost consciousness, she convinced herself that this was her fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:43.39,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that's taken place... why should she care about what becomes of her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.44,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She was just going to vanish without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.42,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.11,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}is{\i0} someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:12.42,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while she was unconscious the world still continued moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.42,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the job doesn't seem like it'll be too difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.55,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,You should still be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.83,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Her feelings, her will, her emotions... To her, none of these things held any meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:11:00.01,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it. I just can't seem to gather the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.16,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying I won't give you the money eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.18,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, if anything happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:08.52,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiki-san, of the Awakusa Group, wouldn't be too happy about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.52,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!{split these -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.95,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time.{split these -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.51,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not busy, or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:16.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm only gonna be able to waste around another two and a half minutes of my life on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.44,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Another guy you shouldn't make an enemy out of is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.25,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.80,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure a skilled transporter like yourself doesn't need someone like me to tell you how to do things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.75,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't need to do anything more than what was requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.31,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rough 'em up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.23,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.90,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The world was still turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:56.83,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Things began to move in a different direction... away from the fate that the girl believed would take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.84,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:22.55,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the {\i1}fuck{\i0}  are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:07.92,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}The text said, "I've been asked to bring you to a certain place."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:13.09,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The bike ran without a sound. Though every so often, it let out a neigh like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:16.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a surreal feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:21.58,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,But the body that she clutched onto confirmed that this was reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:26.26,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl thought about the warmth she was feeling at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:30.87,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What were they thinking, what did they know, and how did they live their life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:34.58,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,When this person looks at her, what did they see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.39,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.97,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Magenta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.10,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:42.98,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Nakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.24,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Nakura who wants to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:55.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you... Were you the person who saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.07,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.64,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.75,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you had it pretty rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:09.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... But why do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:14.10,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I know because the man who arranged to have you kidnapped was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I also arranged to have you rescued. It was all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.23,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.54,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,You were seeking death, yet you got kidnapped instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:28.11,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,You felt scared and a bit frustrated because you still clung on to the hope of surviving, despite the fact that you had decided to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:33.22,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}Yet, in the end, you didn't resist even though you wanted to, because that would've contradicted your previous intentions of dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:37.42,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,so you convinced yourself that this was fate and there was nothing more that you could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:41.00,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,But, now that you know you've been rescued, you feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:44.50,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I just wanted to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.54,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,To put things simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:51.59,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see that utterly speechless look on your face when you realized that someone saw right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.97,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.17,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.43,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:02.58,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,To you this would sound a bit philosophical, but...{this is the best way I figured to time this, but it seems something is missing here... -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.72,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to try to give you a reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.13,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have to be that I just {\i1}love{\i0} humans.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:07.13,0:16:11.24,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so appealing and interesting. I just can't help myself.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:11.63,0:16:16.24,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and just because I like humans, it doesn't mean that I like you personally.
Dialogue: 6,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,That's important to note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.87,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Was everything a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.75,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you finally understand the position you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.29,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:38.56,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people have jumped from here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.93,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I wouldn't really say this place is a well known suicide spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.88,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,it {\i1}is{\i0} high enough that jumping would mean certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.02,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look at that stain down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.45,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,You... think of yourself as someone special, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.19,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.29,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:08.46,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,There's simply no one out there who can just lead an honest life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:12.86,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got one or two secrets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:17.34,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever wondered why your parents are no good compared to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:20.35,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.55,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to summarize things for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.19,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone who cheats or knows someone who's cheating,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:30.61,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,will just keep laughing at boring jokes and continue to eat the overly sweet food, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.04,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:39.45,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what worries they had, all that remains are the bloodstains on the concrete, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.16,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Stains. Indifferent, all of them, without exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.66,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,returned to God as equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.53,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.17,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.36,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:06.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful that I got the chance to see your ugly feelings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:10.11,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually just interested in the things that are involved in your worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.69,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in your worries themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:16.61,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it was fairly boring since you did everything I expected you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:19.86,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, I knew that you never intended to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.11,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:24.00,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun, Magenta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.31,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She hesitated for that brief moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:46.19,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Would she be able to hurt him by killing herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:51.66,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she thought... that maybe she may have just been waiting for an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:55.83,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,For those words, that just so happened to come from a man like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.65,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Without her knowing... something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:39.10,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:58.02,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, she does something uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:06.26,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl thought of her mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.68,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father and his mistress, and about her parents' relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.94,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought about how each of them had a part to their lives that she didn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:21.24,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,About how she didn't know if they were truly as evil, selfish, and hating as she previously believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:26.20,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,About how she didn't know if they were just hiding behind their compromises and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:32.29,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,850)}As she was making her way home, she thought about forgiving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:38.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day... the world had a different look to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.42,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Every person has their own emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.22,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,and single person has their own secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:45.72,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She realized that of course, this was nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.59,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you wherever you wanna go, so today it's your treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.23,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... Well, how about a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:58.15,SUBS-ALT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There are a lot of bookstores. What are you gonna buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.45,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,You could find people like them anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:03.24,SUBS-ALT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um, some manga to read in my spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.93,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, she was sure that they had secrets of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.24,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings that they can never discuss with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.74,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.82,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri-kun, what really happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:09.99,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.91,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you cut class on the first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.42,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.00,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.50,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.96,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.33,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going on with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.14,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a playboy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:31.37,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid in the glasses is in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:36.48,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably just nervous about the dangerous and risky days ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.69,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you put that in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.69,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.69,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,And her, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.94,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,What they see may not be reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:51.91,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}The girl thought to herself that maybe she'll be able to repeat those words to someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:56.96,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}"Because the world isn't as terrible as you think."{if someone can get this transition better, go ahead -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:06.22,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear that you had become a hero of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:13.72,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I entrusted the job to a skilled transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:22.40,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. The informant, Orihara Izaya, isn't {\i1}that{\i0} evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:28.95,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I'm not enough of a humanitarian to stop someone who wants to die, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.45,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun, Ms. Skilled Transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:17.27,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,In Ikebukuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:19.51,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,He also, she also, I also, you also...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:19.51,0:24:22.07,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,came to this town looking for something, seeking something,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:25.06,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:26.65,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:28.11,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Want sushi? It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:30.40,SUBS,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:09.62,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The treacherous sunset wipes away those annoying sweat drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:12.59,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As if it wanted to tear it apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:16.08,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}the machine roars as if it's singing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:22.33,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The quiet fairy is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:28.47,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Atonement is a piece of a broken love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:32.35,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The morning sun rises, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:34.52,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Over the valley of buildings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:38.34,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As long as you believe in it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:42.01,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}tomorrow won't be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:45.10,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The morning sun rises, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:47.20,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Coming out of the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:51.17,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As long as you feel it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.88,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}you'll see that dream isn't meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:01:00.27,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}There's surely something only we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:03.89,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Something that no one will snatch away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:07.63,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fact that this aim isn't meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.86,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The sun rises, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:38.24,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Over the horizon, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:41.95,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As long as you believe in it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:45.33,ENGLISH-OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}that light won't be meaningless.
